import React from 'react';
import { useContext } from 'react';
import { View, Text, ActivityIndicator } from 'react-native';
import { WebSocketContext } from '../Contexts/WebSocketContext'
import { Style } from './Style';

export default function SellBook() {
    const { data } = useContext(WebSocketContext)
    const ask = data.asks;

    return ask ? (
        <View style={Style.rowView}>
        <View style={Style.columnView}>
            <Text style={Style.header}>Price</Text>
            <View style={Style.valueColumn}>
                <Text>{Number(ask[0][0]).toFixed(2)}</Text>
                <Text>{Number(ask[1][0]).toFixed(2)}</Text>
                <Text>{Number(ask[2][0]).toFixed(2)}</Text>
                <Text>{Number(ask[3][0]).toFixed(2)}</Text>
                <Text>{Number(ask[4][0]).toFixed(2)}</Text>
            </View>


        </View>
        <View style={Style.columnView}>
            <Text style={Style.header}>Amount</Text>
            <View style={Style.valueColumn}>
                <Text>{Number(ask[0][1]).toFixed(5)}</Text>
                <Text>{Number(ask[1][1]).toFixed(5)}</Text>
                <Text>{Number(ask[2][1]).toFixed(5)}</Text>
                <Text>{Number(ask[3][1]).toFixed(5)}</Text>
                <Text>{Number(ask[4][1]).toFixed(5)}</Text>
            </View>
        </View>
        <View style={Style.columnView}>
            <Text style={Style.header}>Total</Text>
            <View style={Style.valueColumn}>
                <Text>{Number(ask[0][0] * ask[0][1]).toFixed(5)}</Text>
                <Text>{Number(ask[1][0] * ask[1][1]).toFixed(5)}</Text>
                <Text>{Number(ask[2][0] * ask[2][1]).toFixed(5)}</Text>
                <Text>{Number(ask[3][0] * ask[3][1]).toFixed(5)}</Text>
                <Text>{Number(ask[4][0] * ask[4][1]).toFixed(5)}</Text>
            </View>
        </View>
    </View>
    ) : (
        <View style={Style.container}>
            <ActivityIndicator style={Style.indicatorContainer} size="large" color="" />
        </View>
    )
}
